{"id": "ChIJq8xhPQDHwoAR54RX_no3dOA", "rating": 5, "userRatingCount": 3, "displayName": {"text": "Little Tokyo Farmers' Market", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJq8xhPQDHwoAR54RX_no3dOA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oeWRXczFZbm8yV2tGQ2JWZFhRa2xMVFV4QlZtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Absolutely fantastic new farmer's market every Saturday that started late August 2025.\n\nPros:\n* Very high quality fruit, veggies, etc.\n* Tasty lunch options from various vendors. I like the Latin one.\n* Clean bathrooms inside auditorium.\n* Get secret view of the calming sub-ground level Japanese garden.\n* Close to Metro and public parking lots (maybe $10-15 for whole day).\n* Close to many wonderful places to dine and shop for groceries, anime crap I mean stuff, mochi, etc.\n\nCons:\n* Small. Scale-wise, opposite of the Italian farmer's market in San Diego.\n* Limited meat options for you carnivore bros.\n* For those coming from suburbs, you'll encounter street people. Be brave! You can do it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Absolutely fantastic new farmer's market every Saturday that started late August 2025.\n\nPros:\n* Very high quality fruit, veggies, etc.\n* Tasty lunch options from various vendors. I like the Latin one.\n* Clean bathrooms inside auditorium.\n* Get secret view of the calming sub-ground level Japanese garden.\n* Close to Metro and public parking lots (maybe $10-15 for whole day).\n* Close to many wonderful places to dine and shop for groceries, anime crap I mean stuff, mochi, etc.\n\nCons:\n* Small. Scale-wise, opposite of the Italian farmer's market in San Diego.\n* Limited meat options for you carnivore bros.\n* For those coming from suburbs, you'll encounter street people. Be brave! You can do it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jensen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107265054784165119857/reviews", "photoUri": 